We are a Swiss based quantitative asset management firm.  Polaris Capital Management is owned and managed by principals who between them have over 30 years of experience in investment banking, asset management and technology at some of the world's largest financial institutions and technology companies. We apply a rigorous, scientific method-based approach to investment management. Through the managed accounts platform we provide sophisticated, market-neutral investment strategies to institutions, family offices, funds of funds, and high-net-worth individuals. These products are designed for investors who seek to avoid market drawdowns  and minimize portfolio volatility while generating strong returns.
 










  















 


 




 



 















 



 




 



 















 



 




 



 















 



 




 



 















 



 




 



 















 



 




 



 



 









