Company Overview
Polaris Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to institutions, retirement plans, insurance companies, foundations, endowments, high-net-worth individuals, investment companies, corporations, pension and profit sharing plans, pooled investment vehicles, charitable organizations, state or municipal government entities, and limited partnerships. It manages separate client focused equity portfolios. The firm also manages equity mutual funds and commingled vehicles for its clients. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. The firm invests in stocks of companies across diversified sectors. It primarily invests in value stoc...
Polaris Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to institutions, retirement plans, insurance companies, foundations, endowments, high-net-worth individuals, investment companies, corporations, pension and profit sharing plans, pooled investment vehicles, charitable organizations, state or municipal government entities, and limited partnerships. It manages separate client focused equity portfolios. The firm also manages equity mutual funds and commingled vehicles for its clients. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. The firm invests in stocks of companies across diversified sectors. It primarily invests in value stocks of companies of small-cap companies with market capitalization between $50 million and $2 billion. The firm employs a combination of quantitative and fundamental analysis with bottom-up stock picking approach to create its portfolios. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolios against the MSCI EAFE Index and MSCI World Index. The firm conducts in-house research to make its investments. Polaris Capital Management, LLC was founded in April 1995 and is based in Boston, Massachusetts.
